titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on difenzoquat methyl sulfate.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S5945)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/13/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1995, the duty on 1,2-dimethyl-3,5-diphenylpyrazolium methyl sulfate (also known as difenzoquat methyl sulfate).
